public class Chromosome extends ChromosomeSequence
A ChromosomeSequence is a DNASequence but keeps track of geneSequences
Author:
Scooter Willis Here I modified the original Chromosome class to one which include: coding and noncoding regions + proteins, Christophe Becavin
